{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSPredicate","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSPredicate"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"predicate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the style layer’s predicate to include only the features in the source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer that satisfy a condition that you define. If the style layer initially"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"comes from the style, its predicate corresponds to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"filter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property in the style JSON."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See the “"},{"type":"text","text":"Predicates and Expressions"},{"type":"text","text":"”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"guide for details about the predicate syntax supported by this class."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":3,"text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To filter the layer to include only the features whose "},{"code":"index","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" attribute is 5"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or 10 and whose "},{"code":"ele","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" attribute is at least 1,500, you could create an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NSCompoundPredicate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" along these lines:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let layer = MLNLineStyleLayer(identifier: \"contour\", source: terrain)","layer.sourceLayerIdentifier = \"contours\"","layer.predicate = NSPredicate(format: \"(index == 5 || index == 10) && CAST(ele, 'NSNumber') >=","1500.0\") mapView.style?.addLayer(layer)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The style layer’s predicate."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"predicate"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"predicate","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNVectorStyleLayer(py)predicate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"predicate"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectorstylelayer\/predicate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer\/predicate"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNVectorStyleLayer":{"abstract":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer"},{"type":"text","text":" is an abstract superclass for style layers whose content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is defined by an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectorstylelayer","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNVectorStyleLaye